text: Dinoconda is an S&S; – Sansei Technologies 4th Dimension roller coaster located at Dino Watertown in Jiangsu, China. At the time it was built, it was one of only three regular 4D coasters in the world. It has a capacity of 24 riders per train. ==References== Category:Roller coasters in China Category:4th Dimension roller coasters
title: Dinoconda
